## 1. Lifecycle overview

Every shift has a three-phase lifecycle on the same board row:

**Phase 1 тАФ Close (night, by bartender via app)**
Bartender enters reconciliation data and photos. App computes Variance and writes the row with `Needs Review` or `Balanced` status.

**Phase 2 тАФ Review (optional, by admin)**
If variance тЙа $0, admin reviews and manually sets status to `Approved`. Balanced shifts auto-approve (see automation 5).

**Phase 3 тАФ Deposit (next morning, by admin via app)**
Admin counts handoff cash, takes the deposit to the bank, fills in deposit fields on the same row. Status becomes `Deposited`.

