## 10. Automations

**1. Route variance shifts**
When new item created AND `Variance` тЙа 0 тЖТ move to group `Needs Review`

**2. Route balanced shifts**
When new item created AND `Variance` = 0 тЖТ move to group `This Week`

**3. Auto-approve balanced shifts** (optional тАФ turn on after trust is established)
When new item created AND `Variance` = 0 тЖТ set `Status` to `Approved`

**4. Notify admin on large close variance**
When new item created AND (`Variance` > 20 OR `Variance` < -20) тЖТ notify Gentry

**5. Route to Ready to Deposit**
When `Status` changes to `Approved` тЖТ move to group `Ready to Deposit`

**6. Route to Deposited**
When `Status` changes to `Deposited` тЖТ move to group `Deposited`

**7. Flag deposit variance**
When `Deposit Variance` тЙа 0 AND `Deposited $` not empty тЖТ notify Gentry

**8. Flag Main/Patio bank shortage**
When `Drawer` is `Main Bar` AND `Bank Transferred to Patio` > 0 AND (`Bank Returned from Patio` < `Bank Transferred to Patio`) тЖТ notify Gentry with message "Patio bank short on [Shift]"

**9. Morning deposit reminder** (Phase 3)
Daily at 8 AM, if items exist in `Ready to Deposit` тЖТ notify Gentry

**10. Archive old entries**
When `Deposit Date` > 90 days ago тЖТ move to group `Archive`

