## 11. App responsibilities summary (Phase 2+)

**Bartender home screen:**
- "Log Patio Handoff" button (Main bartenders only тАФ app detects from context)
- "Close Drawer" button тЖТ launches close flow

**Close flow тАФ Main Bar:**
- Form with all close fields
- Shows "$500 float" reminder
- If any unconsumed handoffs for today exist, adds a section: "Patio handoff reconciliation"
  - Transferred to Patio: [prefilled, read-only]
  - Returned from Patio: [enter amount]
- Photo capture
- Submit тЖТ app computes Expected, Variance, To Deposit, writes to Monday, marks handoff as consumed

**Close flow тАФ Patio Bar:**
- App looks for matching unconsumed handoff тЖТ if none, blocks with error
- Form shows "Opening Bank from Main: $200" read-only
- All standard close fields
- New field: "Returning to Main: $___"
- Photo capture
- Submit тЖТ app updates handoff row with amountReturned, writes Patio close to Monday

**Admin deposit flow:**
- "Ready to Deposit" queue from Monday
- Tap a shift тЖТ deposit form
- `To Deposit $` read-only, `Deposited $` input, date, two photos, notes
- Submit тЖТ app computes Deposit Variance, sets Status to `Deposited`

